  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The investigators prospectively enrolled 64 early PD patients (less than 3 years after the
      first symptom) in order to prospectively assess the natural history of non-dopaminergic
      symptoms.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      Patients were evaluated at baseline and after 2 years in off drug condition. Clinical,
      psychological, neuropsychological evaluations, functional respiratory evaluation, swallowing
      video fluoroscopy, dysarthria, gait and axial disorders.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
